{
  "texts": [
    "All models were trained on a single A100-40GB GPU, except for Vicuna SFT which was trained on 4 GPUs using Fully Sharded Data Parallel (FSDP) (Artetxe et al., 2022).",
    "Every model checkpoint is evaluated on the validation set, with BERTScore being used on this set for model selection.",
    "The AdamW optimizer (Loshchilov and Hutter, 2019) was used to train all models.",
    "A more detailed description can be found in Appendix B.3.",
    "We begin by evaluating the models' ability to generate responses in the context of procedural plans."
  ]
}